RACE.FOOTNOTES: TOSS OF FATE pressed the pace two wide into the far turn, bid in late turn to gain a short lead, lost the lead to the rallying runner-up outside the eighth pole then battled back to edged up late. BLUEMOON JUSTICE was unhurried while off the inside, bid through the four path in late turn, came into the lane under a drive to gain the lead outside the eighth pole then could not hold the winner safe. UPHOLD raced three wide through the first turn, continued to stalk the pace while in the three path, bid three wide into the far turn, continued as a contender into the lane then weakened while finishing far in front of the others.
